# Vercel Environment Variables - Ready to Import
# =====================================================
# 
# HOW TO USE:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to something like vercel.env
# 2. Replace the placeholder with your real key
# 3. Go to Vercel Dashboard → Your Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# 4. Click the "Import" button and upload the file
# 5. Make sure it applies to Production, Preview, and Development
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit a file with your real secret key to GitHub!

NEXT_PUBLIC_KIT_KEY=your_real_circle_app_kit_key_here
